    "自定义此连接在 Finder 中显示的名称。留空将根据路径自动生成；名称不能与其它连接重复。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Customize the name shown for this connection in Finder. Leave empty to generate one from the path; the name must be unique."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "自定义此连接在 Finder 中显示的名称。留空将根据路径自动生成；名称不能与其它连接重复。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
