    "开机自动挂载" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Auto-mount at Login"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开机自动挂载"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "所有自动挂载方法均失败。请在系统设置中启用「SMBKeep File System」文件系统扩展后重试。\n\n扩展 Bundle ID: %@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All automatic mount methods failed. Enable the “SMBKeep File System” file system extension in System Settings, then try again.\n\nExtension Bundle ID: %@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "所有自动挂载方法均失败。请在系统设置中启用「SMBKeep File System」文件系统扩展后重试。\n\n扩展 Bundle ID: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "打开系统设置" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Open System Settings"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "打开系统设置"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Mount"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载失败，疑似 FSKit 守护进程状态陈旧。\n\n请在「终端」中执行下方命令重启 fskitd，然后重新挂载（多数情况下并不需要这一步）：\n%@\n\n扩展 Bundle ID: %@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The mount failed, likely due to stale FSKit daemon state.\n\nRun the command below in Terminal to restart fskitd, then try mounting again (this is rarely necessary):\n%@\n\nExtension Bundle ID: %@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载失败，疑似 FSKit 守护进程状态陈旧。\n\n请在「终端」中执行下方命令重启 fskitd，然后重新挂载（多数情况下并不需要这一步）：\n%@\n\n扩展 Bundle ID: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载失败疑似由 FSKit 守护进程状态陈旧导致。请在「终端」中执行下方命令重启后重新挂载（多数情况下并不需要这一步）。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The mount likely failed because of stale FSKit daemon state. Run the command below in Terminal to restart it, then try mounting again (this is rarely necessary)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载失败疑似由 FSKit 守护进程状态陈旧导致。请在「终端」中执行下方命令重启后重新挂载（多数情况下并不需要这一步）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载完成后可以放心退出 App：已挂载的卷宗由系统的文件系统扩展维持，关闭本 App 不会卸载它们。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Once mounted, you can safely quit the app. Mounted volumes are kept active by the system's file system extension and stay available even after this app is closed."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载完成后可以放心退出 App：已挂载的卷宗由系统的文件系统扩展维持，关闭本 App 不会卸载它们。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载点已经不在 mount 表中，按已卸载处理\n" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The mount point is no longer in the mount table; treating it as unmounted.\n"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载点已经不在 mount 表中，按已卸载处理\n"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载点已经卸载，忽略卸载命令错误\n" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The mount point is already unmounted; ignoring the unmount command error.\n"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载点已经卸载，忽略卸载命令错误\n"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "挂载需要在「系统设置」中启用「SMBKeep File System」扩展。点按下方按钮前往，打开对应开关后再回到本 App 重新挂载。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Mounting requires enabling the “SMBKeep File System” extension in System Settings. Tap the button below to open it, turn on the switch, then come back and mount again."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "挂载需要在「系统设置」中启用「SMBKeep File System」扩展。点按下方按钮前往，打开对应开关后再回到本 App 重新挂载。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
