    "登录后自动补挂载上次已挂载的连接" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Automatically remount previously mounted connections after login."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "登录后自动补挂载上次已挂载的连接"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "登录项启动时会在后台自动挂载；若 App 被系统恢复或手动打开，也会补挂载尚未挂上的连接。密码保存在钥匙串中，不会写入任何启动脚本。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When launched as a login item, SMBKeep mounts in the background. If the app is restored by the system or opened manually, it also remounts any pending connections. Passwords are stored in the Keychain and are never written to any launch script."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "登录项启动时会在后台自动挂载；若 App 被系统恢复或手动打开，也会补挂载尚未挂上的连接。密码保存在钥匙串中，不会写入任何启动脚本。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "登录项设置失败：%@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Failed to configure login item: %@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "登录项设置失败：%@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "确定要删除连接「%@」吗？此操作不可撤销。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Are you sure you want to delete the connection “%@”? This action cannot be undone."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "确定要删除连接「%@」吗？此操作不可撤销。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
